@Gradify_HostAddress = http://localhost:5135

### Register a new user
POST {{Gradify_HostAddress}}/api/auth/register?role=Student
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "Username": "studentuser",
  "Email": "studentuser@example.com",
  "Password": "Password123!"
}

### Register a new teacher
POST {{Gradify_HostAddress}}/api/auth/register?role=Teacher
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "Username": "teacheruser",
  "Email": "teacheruser@example.com",
  "Password": "Password123!"
}

### Login to get a token
POST {{Gradify_HostAddress}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "Username": "studentuser",
  "Password": "Password123!"
}

### Upload a file to a specific class (requires Bearer token)
POST {{Gradify_HostAddress}}/api/files/upload?classId=1
Content-Type: multipart/form-data
Authorization: Bearer <your_token_here>

Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="homework.pdf"

### List files in a specific class
GET {{Gradify_HostAddress}}/api/files/1
Authorization: Bearer <your_token_here>

### Download a specific file from a class
GET {{Gradify_HostAddress}}/api/files/download/1/1
Authorization: Bearer <your_token_here>

### Delete a specific file from a class (requires Bearer token)
DELETE {{Gradify_HostAddress}}/api/files/1/1
Authorization: Bearer <your_token_here>
